name: Dagger
description:
Used for self-defense. Although its blade is longer than
that of a normal knife, its attack power is rather low.

name: Mythril Knife
description:
A sturdy, well-balanced knife forged from the featherlight
metal known as mythril.

name: Blind Knife
description:
A knife quenched in an insidious poison that robs its
victim of sight.

name: Mage Masher
description:
Created especially for the purpose of fighting mages,
this knife has the power to silence its target.

name: Platinum Dagger
description:
A knife with a blade made of a lustrous white alloy
of mythril and platinum.

name: Main Gauche
description:
This knife gives the wielder a good chance of blocking
attacks, making it useful for both offense and defense.

name: Orichalcum Dirk
description:
A knife made of an exceedingly hard metal.
Light and sharp.

name: Assassin's Dagger
description:
Popular among assassins, this dagger has the power
to doom its victims to certain death.

name: Air Knife
description:
This knife's special wave-shaped blade creates a vacuum
when swung through the air, increasing its killing power.

name: Zwill Straightblade
description:
A knife manufactured in a region renowned for its
blades.

name: Ninja Blade
description:
A sword specially tailored to the needs of ninjas.
Its blade is shorter than that of the average sword.

name: Kunai
description: A multipurpose sword for ninjas.

name: Kodachi
description:
This sword's short, lightweight blade makes it very easy
to carry.

name: Ninja Longblade
description:
A sword with a longer blade than that of a normal ninja
sword, making it more suitable for use in battle.

name: Spellbinder
description:
A sword with the power to stop its targets in their
tracks, preventing them from taking any actions.

name: Sasuke's Blade
description: A legendary ninja's sword.

name: Iga Blade
description:
An exquisitely crafted ninja sword that was once used
by a secret society.

name: Koga Blade
description:
A powerful ninja sword that was once used by a
secret society.

name: Broadsword
description:
This broad-bladed sword is suited for large slashing
strokes. It is inexpensive, but not particularly powerful.

name: Longsword
description:
This straight and sharp double-edged blade can be used for
either stabbing or slashing.

name: Iron Sword
description:
This sword has a broad and sturdy blade, but its
iron construction makes it very heavy.

name: Mythril Sword
description:
A sword forged from the metal known as mythril.
Its brilliantly shining blade is incredibly lightweight.

name: Blood Sword
description:
The blade of this sword is a deep crimson, as if it were
drenched in blood. It is cruelly sharp.

name: Coral Sword
description:
The handle of this single-edged sword has been decorated
with intricate coral piecework.

name: Ancient Sword
description:
A sword constructed using ancient techniques that
have long since perished from the world.

name: Sleep Blade
description: A wide-bladed sword with a midnight blue handle.

name: Platinum Sword
description:
A shining sword made of a lustrous white alloy of mythril
and platinum. Its broad blade is wickedly sharp.

name: Diamond Sword
description:
The countless tiny diamonds embedded into this sword's
blade saw into its victims, causing great damage.

name: Icebrand
description: A sword with a transparent blade that resembles ice.

name: Runeblade
description: A sword inscribed with ancient runes.

name: Nagnarok
description:
This dark blade is mentioned in legends about the end
of the world.

name: Materia Blade
description: A sword of extraplanar origin.

name: Defender
description:
A broad-bladed knight's sword made from hardened steel.
Jewels have been embedded in its rounded pommel.

name: Save the Queen
description: A knight's sword given as a symbol of an oath of fealty.

name: Excalibur
description:
It is said that only the true heir to the throne can
wield this legendary knight's sword.

name: Ragnarok
description:
This knight's sword is mentioned in tales about the end
of the world.

name: Chaos Blade
description:
This holy knight's sword is said to have been a gift
from the gods themselves.

name: Ashura
description: A katana with a brilliant white blade.

name: Kotetsu
description:
A katana whose blade is adorned with a breathtaking
carving of a tiger.

name: Osafune
description:
A katana with a blade forged of the finest iron sand
by master swordsmith Nagamitsu Osafune.

name: Murasame
description:
Referred to as a demon sword, this katana's keen
blade showers blood upon the battlefield.

name: Ama-no-Murakamo
description:
This katana's design was inspired by a legendary blade said
to have been plucked from the tail of a marauding dragon.

name: Kiyomori
description:
This exquisitely crafted katana has a beautifully
patterned blade and an incredible cutting edge.

name: Muramasa
description:
Referred to as a demon sword, this katana was said
to drink the blood of countless enemies.

name: Kiku-ichimonji
description: A katana with a hilt in the shape of a chrysanthemum.

name: Masamune
description:
This katana's sheath is inlaid with beautiful patterns.
It is the life's work of a master swordsmith.

name: Chirijiraden
description: This katana is decorated with intricate designs.

name: Battle Axe
description:
A battle axe with a long handle. Designed for two-handed
use, it can easily chop off an enemy's limbs.

name: Giant's Axe
description:
An axe with a large head. Much bigger than the traditional
woodman's axe, hence its name.

name: Slasher
description:
This axe not only has impressive destructive power,
but can also slow the actions of its target.

name: Rod
description: A rod fashioned from evergreen wood.

name: Thunder Rod
description: A rod imbued with the power of thunder.

name: Flame Rod
description: A rod imbued with the power of fire.

name: Ice Rod
description: A rod imbued with the power of ice.

name: Poison Rod
description: A rod with a poisoned tip.

name: Wizard's Rod
description: A rod that enhances the magickal potency of its wielder.

name: Dragon Rod
description:
A rod wielded by a dragon master. Its tip is made from
carved dragon bone.

name: Rod of Faith
description:
This rod purges doubt from those it touches, turning
them into pillars of faith.

name: Oak Staff
description: A staff made from sturdy oak.

name: White Staff
description: A staff carried by members of the clergy.

name: Healing Staff
description:
A staff imbued with the power of spirits.
Has the power to restore HP to those it hits.

name: Serpent Staff
description: A staff with a giant serpent scale embedded in its tip.

name: Mage's Staff
description:
This cypress staff increases the magick power
of its owner.

name: Golden Staff
description: A shiny staff decorated with gold.

name: Zeus Mace
description: A staff that increases the strength of its user.

name: Staff of the Magi
description: An ordinary wooden staff that one might find anywhere.

name: Iron Flail
description:
A weapon comprised of a large iron head attached to a
long wooden handle.

name: Flame Mace
description: The head of this large mace is enveloped in flames.

name: Morning Star
description:
A large spiked metal ball attached by chain to a wooden
pole.

name: Scorpion Tail
description: A large morning star with a single spike attached to it.

name: Romandan Pistol
description:
A firearm brought to Ivalice from the northern
country of Romanda.

name: Mythril Gun
description:
The barrel of this firearm has been fashioned from
mythril.

name: Stoneshooter
description: A firearm with the power to petrify.

name: Glacial Gun
description: A firearm that shoots freezing bullets.

name: Blaze Gun
description: A firearm that shoots flaming bullets.

name: Blaster
description: A firearm that shoots electrically charged bullets.

name: Bowgun
description:
A crossbow that can be fired with one hand.
Uses shorter bolts than a traditional crossbow.

name: Knightslayer
description:
This crossbow fires specially fashioned bolts that 
contain a dose of blinding poison.

name: Crossbow
description:
The firing mechanism of this crossbow has been
improved upon, increasing its attack power.

name: Poison Bow
description:
A crossbow that fires bolts dipped in poison.
Includes a mechanism for handling the poisoned bolts.

name: Hunting Bow
description: A crossbow mainly employed for hunting monsters.

name: Gastrophetes
description:
The most powerful crossbow ever created.
Its unusual size gives it a very strong recoil.

name: Longbow
description:
The most common type of bow. It has a long range and is
quite durable.

name: Silver Bow
description:
A bow adorned with silver decorations. Thin metal plates
help strengthen its wooden frame.

name: Ice Bow
description: A bow that shoots freezing arrows.

name: Lightning Bow
description:
This bow imbues arrows with the power and speed
of lightning.

name: Windslash Bow
description:
Arrows shot by this bow fly at extremely high speeds. The
vacuum created by their flight increases their damage.

name: Mythril Bow
description: A bow strengthened by thin plates of mythril.

name: Artemis Bow
description: The bow of the goddess of the hunt.

name: Yoichi Bow
description:
The bow of a legendary archer. Its unusual size gives it
incredible power.

name: Perseus Bow
description:
The bow of a mythical hero. It is constructed entirely
of metal and requires great strength to pull back.

name: Lamia's Harp
description:
The strains of this harp can affect one's very soul.
Causes confusion in the listener.

name: Bloodstring Harp
description: A harp with a rich timbre and wide tonal range.

name: Faerie Harp
description: The pure sound of this harp can charm its user's enemies.

name: Battle Folio
description: A book made for battle.

name: Bestiary
description: A thick book describing various beasts.

name: Papyrus Codex
description: An ancient text bound in stone.

name: Omnilex
description: A book said to contain all words in all languages.

name: Javelin
description:
A light and inexpensive spear. Allows the wielder
to attack enemies within a range of two tiles.

name: Spear
description:
The most commonly used type of spear.
Distinguished by its especially long reach.

name: Mythril Spear
description:
The tip of this spear is made from the valuable metal
known as mythril.

name: Partisan
description:
A polearm tipped with a broad, double-edged blade.
Its design increases the damage it causes.

name: Obelisk
description: A hefty spear fitted with an obelisk-shaped head.

name: Holy Lance
description: This sacred weapon shines a brilliant blue.

name: Dragon Whisker
description:
A spear made from a mysterious material that is neither
wood nor metal. Some say it is a dragon's whisker.

name: Javelin (Strong)
description: This spear has unmatched attack power.

name: Cypress Pole
description: A pole carved from the wood of a cypress.

name: Battle Bamboo
description:
A thin and supple bamboo pole that bends lithely
when swung through the air.

name: Musk Pole
description:
A pole crafted from wood that emits a musky scent.
It is in the shape of a large ladle.

name: Iron Fan
description:
The ribs of this enormous fan are made of iron.
When folded up, it may be employed as a pole in battle.

name: Gokuu Pole
description:
One strike from this pole can cause the target to
lose his faith.

name: Ivory Pole
description:
A pole made from specially treated ivory. It is
surprisingly strong, despite its fragile appearance.

name: Eight-fluted Pole
description:
A shaft of boxwood, carved into a hexagonal shape
and reinforced with metal plates.

name: Whale Whisker
description:
A pole made from a dark material that is neither wood 
nor metal. Some say it is a dire whale's whisker.

name: Croakadile Bag
description: An expensive designer handbag made of croakadile skin.

name: Fallingstar Bag
description: A custom-made handbag designed for battle.

name: Pantherskin Bag
description: The design of this handbag is simple, yet fashionable.

name: Hydrascale Bag
description: A handbag studded with scales from a hydra.

name: Damask Cloth
description:
This cloth is thick and brilliantly colored, making it perfect
for use in carpets.

name: Cashmere
description:
This warm and flexible woolen fabric is exquisitely soft to
the touch.

name: Wyrmweave Silk
description:
A special process has been used to make this thin, smooth
silk exceptionally durable.

name: Shuriken
description:
A throwing weapon for ninjas.
It spins in the air before hitting its target.

name: Fuma Shuriken
description:
A pinwheel-shaped throwing star that flies at very
high speeds.

name: Yagyu Darkrood
description:
A cross-shaped throwing star used by a famous ninja
school. Its blades are serrated for maximum damage.

name: Flameburst Bomb
description:
An explosive sphere that deals fire damage
when thrown.

name: Snowmelt Bomb
description:
An explosive sphere that deals water damage
when thrown.

name: Spark Bomb
description:
An explosive sphere that deals lightning damage
when thrown.

name: Escutcheon (weak)
description:
The most inexpensive shield available. As expected,
its defensive abilities are lacking.

name: Buckler
description:
A small shield for close-quarters fighting. Though
easy to use, its ability to block attacks is lacking.

name: Bronze Shield
description:
This bronze shield is rather small, allowing the user
to deftly block his opponent's attacks.

name: Round Shield
description:
The surface of this small, sturdy shield has been
inlaid with a complex ornamental design.

name: Mythril Shield
description:
A shield constructed of the featherlight metal known
as mythril. It is surprisingly light and easy to wield.

name: Golden Shield
description:
This mythril shield has been decorated with gold accents
and provides excellent protection against physical attacks.

name: Ice Shield
description:
This mythril shield is inlaid with pale blue gemstones
that seem to emit a frigid aura.

name: Flame Shield
description:
This mythril shield is inlaid with deep crimson gemstones
that seem to dance with the power of flame.

name: Aegis Shield
description:
This shield resembles a breastplate worn by a god.
It enhances the user's magickal capabilities.

name: Diamond Shield
description:
A shield adorned with brilliant, incredibly hard gems that
help protect the user from magicks.

name: Platinum Shield
description:
This brilliant shield has been forged from a lustrous
white alloy of mythril and platinum.

name: Crystal Shield
description:
This shield has been inlaid with crystalline jewels
discovered deep within the earth.

name: Genji Shield
description:
A pitch-black shield made by foreign craftsmen.
It is made of iron and has a unique shape.

name: Kaiser Shield
description:
A shield bearing the name of an ancient emperor. It boosts
the damage dealt by certain elemental magicks.

name: Venetian Shield
description:
A shield that has been brilliantly colored using special dyes
and pigments. It halves damage from the primary elements.

name: Escutcheon (strong)
description: This shield's blocking capabilities are nearly unrivaled.

name: Leather Helm
description:
This leather helm has been treated with a special resin,
making it sturdy yet flexible.

name: Bronze Helm
description: An ordinary bronze helm.

name: Iron Helm
description: A sturdy iron helm.

name: Barbut
description:
This helm covers the entire head, save for a T-shaped
cutout for the wearer's face.

name: Mythril Helm
description:
A helm made from the valuable metal known as mythril.
It is very sturdy and surprisingly lightweight.

name: Golden Helm
description: A mythril helm with gold accents.

name: Close Helmet
description:
This helm completely protects the head and neck,
and its front guard protects the face as well.

name: Diamond Helm
description:
A close helmet adorned with magickal jewels of
extraordinary hardness.

name: Platinum Helm
description:
This brilliant helm has been forged from a lustrous
white alloy of mythril and platinum.

name: Circlet
description:
Jewels have been embedded around the front of this helm.
The design exposes the wearer's ears, making it lighter.

name: Crystal Helm
description:
This platinum helm has been inlaid with crystalline jewels
discovered deep within the earth.

name: Genji Helm
description:
A helm forged by foreign craftsmen. It is made of iron
and has a unique shape.

name: Grand Helm
description: A helm that wards off certain status ailments.

name: Leather Cap
description: A hat crafted from tanned leather.

name: Plumed Hat
description: A sturdy hat adorned with a fluffy white feather.

name: Red Hood
description: A hat made from deep red cloth.

name: Headgear
description: A leather hood that protects the wearer's head and ears.

name: Wizard's Hat
description: A hat adorned with a magick symbol.

name: Green Beret
description: A beret worn by units assigned to special missions.

name: Headband
description:
Headgear made from a twisted towel.
It seems to strengthen the wearer's resolve.

name: Celebrant's Miter
description:
An elaborately decorated hat employed by the clergy in
religious ceremonies.

name: Black Cowl
description: A pitch-black cloth hat.

name: Gold Hairpin
description: A hairpin beautifully decorated with gold inlay.

name: Lambent Hat
description:
The crystals decorating this hat increase the wearer's
agility and magickal attack power.

name: Thief's Cap
description:
A hat that increases agility and protects against certain
status ailments.

name: Cachusha
description: A hairband that prevents an array of status effects.

name: Barette
description: A hairpin that prevents an array of status effects.

name: Ribbon
description: A ribbon that protects against status effects.

name: Leather Armor
description: Armor made from layers of tanned leather.

name: Linen Cuirass
description: Linen armor with a bronze breastplate.

name: Bronze Armor
description: Simply fashioned bronze armor.

name: Chainmail
description: Armor fashioned from countless interlocking metal rings.

name: Mythril Armor
description:
Armor made from the valuable metal known as mythril.
It is surprisingly light and sturdy.

name: Plate Mail
description:
The unique design of this mythril armor greatly
increases its protective qualities.

name: Golden Armor
description: Improved plate mail that has been decorated with gold.

name: Diamond Armor
description:
Armor that has been reinforced with incredibly hard
gemstones.

name: Platinum Armor
description:
Brilliantly shining armor made of a lustrous white alloy
of mythril and platinum.

name: Carabiner Mail
description:
Thick mythril armor designed to withstand even the
most intense shocks.

name: Crystal Mail
description:
Platinum armor reinforced in places with crystalline
gemstones found deep within the earth.

name: Genji Armor
description:
Red enameled armor made by foreign craftsmen.
It completely protects the torso and back.

name: Mirror Mail
description:
Armor with the power to reflect magick used on the
wearer.

name: Maximillian
description:
Top-grade armor made with advanced techniques.
The materials and design make it exceedingly strong.

name: Clothing
description:
Made for use in battle, this is sturdier than normal
clothing.

name: Leather Clothing
description: Leather clothing made for battle.

name: Leather Plate
description:
The many layers of leather used in this battle clothing
make it very sturdy.

name: Ringmail
description: A shirt made of countless interlocking metal rings.

name: Mythril Vest
description: A vest with many small mythril plates sewn into it.

name: Adamant Vest
description: A vest with plates of an incredibly hard metal sewn into it.

name: Wizard Clothing
description: A hooded outfit often worn by mages.

name: Brigandine
description:
A cloth garment reinforced with plates of a mythril
and platinum alloy.

name: Jujitsu Gi
description:
A singlet created by foreign craftsmen and favored by
practitioners of the martial arts.

name: Power Garb
description:
A supportive garment that enhances the wearer's
fighting capabilities.

name: Gaia Gear
description:
Clothing made from brilliantly patterned material.
It confers the protection of the earth to the wearer.

name: Ninja Gear
description: This ninja clothing is suited to covert missions.

name: Black Garb
description: Pitch-black clothing made for battle.

name: Rubber Suit
description:
Clothing made from an unusual resin that perfectly
fits the contours of the wearer's body.

name: Hempen Robe
description: A simple robe made from a single sheet of linen cloth.

name: Silken Robe
description: A smooth robe made from layers of silk cloth.

name: Wizard's Robe
description: A hooded robe that completely covers the wearer's body.

name: Chameleon Robe
description: A robe dyed with pigments made from shining green stones.

name: White Robe
description:
These pure white vestments halve damage taken from
the primary elements.

name: Black Robe
description:
These pitch-black vestments increase damage inflicted
by magicks of the primary elements.

name: Luminous Robe
description:
The material in this robe has been woven from threads
that glow faintly with magick.

name: Lordly Robe
description: Luxurious robe worn by high-ranking nobles.

name: Battle Boots
description: Battle boots made from layers of leather.

name: Spiked Boots
description:
The spikes along the bottoms of these boots improve
the wearer's footing, allowing him or her to jump farther.

name: Germinas Boots
description:
Boots that fit the feet perfectly, increasing the wearer's
mobility.

name: Rubber Boots
description:
These resin boots conform perfectly to the shape of the
wearer's feet, negating lightning-based magick damage.

name: Winged Boots
description: Lightweight boots decorated with fluffy feathers.

name: Hermes Shoes
description: Expensive shoes made by a famous cobbler.

name: Red Shoes
description: Shoes that have been dyed a deep crimson.

name: Power Gauntlet
description: A sturdy glove that increases weapon attack power.

name: Genji Glove
description: A vermillion glove made by a foreign craftsman.

name: Magepower Glove
description: A glove that boosts the wearer's magickal attack power.

name: Bracer
description: A thin leather bracer.

name: Reflect Ring
description:
A ring engraved with arcane symbols that can reflect
magick cast upon the wearer.

name: Protect Ring
description: A ring forged from metal imbued with magick.

name: Magick Ring
description: A ring inlaid with a magickal gemstone.

name: Cursed Ring
description: A ring forged from metal inhabited by spirits.

name: Angel Ring
description: A ring that bestows an angel's aegis upon its owner.

name: Diamond Bracelet
description: A bracelet embedded with shining magickal jewels.

name: Jade Armlet
description: A bracelet embedded with well-polished green jewels.

name: Japa Mala
description:
A string of prayer beads made from 108 fruits of the
sacred fig tree.

name: Nu Khai Armband
description:
An armband worn during a ceremony to worship gods of
darkness.

name: Guardian Bracelet
description: A bracelet embedded with deep crimson jewels.

name: Shoulder Cape
description: A small woolen cape.

name: Leather Cloak
description: A sturdy leather cloak.

name: Mage's Cloak
description: A hooded cloak often worn by mages.

name: Elven Cloak
description:
A short cloak made of thin material that has been
imbued with magickal power.

name: Vampire Cape
description:
The outside of this cloak is black, while the inside is deep
crimson.

name: Featherweave Cape
description: This cloak is as light and soft as a feather.

name: Invisibility Cloak
description:
This cloak makes the wearer invisible—until he or she
is discovered.

name: Chantage
description: A perfume with a soothing scent.

name: Cherche
description: A perfume with a refreshing fragrance.

name: Septième
description: A perfume with an otherworldly aroma.

name: Sortilége
description: A perfume with a rich redolence.

name: Potion
description:
Medicine that restores HP.
Deals damage when used against the undead.

name: Hi-Potion
description:
Medicine that restores HP.
More effective than a standard potion.

name: X-Potion
description:
Medicine that restores HP.
More effective than a hi-potion.

name: Ether
description: Medicine that restores MP.

name: Hi-Ether
description:
Medicine that restores MP.
More effective than a standard ether.

name: Elixir
description: Valuable medicine that fully restores both HP and MP.

name: Antidote
description: Medicine that neutralizes poison from enemy attacks.

name: Eye Drops
description:
Medicine that restores sight to those blinded by
magick or other causes.

name: Echo Herbs
description:
Medicine that restores the power of speech to
silenced units, allowing them to cast spells.

name: Maiden's Kiss
description:
Medicine that restores a unit who
has been transformed into a toad.

name: Gold Needle
description:
A tool that restores a unit who has been turned to stone.
It breaks after one use.

name: Holy Water
description:
Holy water that restores life to a unit who has been
touched by the curse of undeath.

name: Remedy
description: A nostrum that cures all manner of status effects.

name: Phoenix Down
description:
Down feathers with the power to restore a unit
who has fallen in battle. Consumed after one use.

name: Chaosbringer
description:
The wielder of this sword bears the sins of his
previous lives, robbing him or her of all hope.

name: Deathbringer
description:
This sword brings death to all those who kill in the
name of truth and justice.

name: Arondight
description:
It is said that a witch bestowed this sword to a
knight who died an unnatural death.

name: Balmung
description:
A sword said to have been wielded by a hero from
the north. A blue jewel is embedded in its broad handle.

name: Valhalla
description:
A tainted blade spoken of in legends about the end of
the world, said to feed upon the souls of its victims.

name: Moonblade
description: A sword that glitters cruelly like a crescent moon.

name: Onion Sword
description:
A blade forged for swordsmen who have mastered every
technique and achieved knighthood's most exalted rank.

name: Ras Algethi
description:
A firearm named for Ras Algethi, the star that forms
the Kneeler's head.

name: Fomalhaut
description:
A firearm named for the brightest star in the Whale's
Maw.

name: Francisca
description: This axe's small size belies its incredible destructive power.

name: Golden Axe
description:
An axe said to have been a gift from spirits inhabiting
a spring. Only the righteous may wield it.

name: Orochi
description: A katana that strikes like a savage serpent.

name: Moonsilk Blade
description:
The creator of this masterpiece learned the art of
swordcraft in a faraway land.

name: Nirvana
description: A staff that can only be mastered by the enlightened.

name: Dreamwaker
description: A powerful staff said to give life to its owner's dreams.

name: Stardust Rod
description: A rod tipped with a meteorite fragment.

name: Crown Scepter
description: A magicked rod wielded by members of the royal guard.

name: Vesper
description: A weapon named after the evenstar.

name: Sagittarius Bow
description: An enormous bow that fires meteor-like arrows.

name: Durandal
description: A holy knight's sword said to have been forged by spirits.

name: Gae Bolg
description:
A spear said to have been wielded by a child of the
gods. Merely lifting it requires great strength.

name: Gungnir
description: A spear with the power to pierce anything.

name: Onion Shield
description:
A shield forged for swordsmen who have mastered every
technique and achieved knighthood's most exalted rank.

name: Reverie Shield
description: A shield imbued with resistance to various attacks.

name: Vanguard Helm
description:
A helm passed down from one veteran warrior to the next.
Every pit and scratch recalls a pitched battle.

name: Onion Helm
description:
A helm forged for swordsmen who have mastered every
technique and achieved knighthood's most exalted rank.

name: Acacia Hat
description:
A hat that increases agility and protects against
certain status effects.

name: Brass Coronet
description: A crown that boosts the potency of the wearer's magicks.

name: Grand Armor
description:
Legendary armor given by the gods to a knight in honor of
his service. Confers divine protection to the wearer.

name: Onion Armor
description:
Armor forged for swordsmen who have mastered every
technique and achieved knighthood's most exalted rank.

name: Minerva Bustier
description:
Clothing blessed by a goddess. It provides protection
against various elemental magicks.

name: Mirage Vest
description:
A vest designed to increase the user's mobility.
Prevents several status ailments.

name: Brave Suit
description:
This battle garb is rumored to prevent its wearer from
defeat as long as he or she has the will to fight.

name: Sage's Robe
description:
A robe woven from threads that shimmer in all colors of
the rainbow. Halves damage taken from elemental magick.

name: Gaius Caligae
description: Military sandals bearing the name of an ancient emperor.

name: Brigand's Gloves
description: Gloves that increase the wearer's mobility.

name: Onion Gloves
description:
Gloves forged for swordsmen who have mastered every
technique and achieved knighthood's most exalted rank.

name: Empyreal Armband
description: An armband that contains the power of the stars.

name: Tynar Rouge
description:
Magickal lip rouge from the popular Feyforge brand.
It is a limited-edition product, making it difficult for
even the richest noblewomen to obtain.

name: Sage's Ring
description: A ring bearing a magickal jewel.
